                                                                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="16870788" author="ben.manes" created="Mon, 24 Jun 2019 03:49:52 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;If you implement CacheLoader, you can override asyncReload to supply the refresh future tied to a different executor.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="16871004" author="beobal" created="Mon, 24 Jun 2019 09:19:32 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=ben.manes&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;ben.manes&quot;&gt;ben.manes&lt;/a&gt;&#160;can&apos;t we just supply a different executor here: &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/cassandra/blob/trunk/src/java/org/apache/cassandra/auth/AuthCache.java#L221&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/cassandra/blob/trunk/src/java/org/apache/cassandra/auth/AuthCache.java#L221&lt;/a&gt;&#160;?&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="16871194" author="ben.manes" created="Mon, 24 Jun 2019 13:20:06 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Oh of course. There was a request at some point to not do that, so I was mentioning the trick in case if you preferred the mixed behavior.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17305058" author="beobal" created="Fri, 19 Mar 2021 17:19:09 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I had forgotten about this, but we ought to fix it before rc. Reloading eligible items on a thread servicing user requests can cause timeouts and unavailables. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/beobal/cassandra/commits/15177-trunk&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;patch&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&quot;https://app.circleci.com/pipelines/github/beobal/cassandra?branch=cci%2F15177-trunk&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;circle&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&quot;https://ci-cassandra.apache.org/view/patches/job/Cassandra-devbranch/500&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;ci-c.a.o&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17305157" author="brandon.williams" created="Fri, 19 Mar 2021 19:45:34 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;+1&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17306862" author="blerer" created="Tue, 23 Mar 2021 07:57:18 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The patch looks good to me.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17306946" author="beobal" created="Tue, 23 Mar 2021 10:07:14 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks, committed to trunk in &lt;tt&gt;d656f8ac012f4577d22ed7bd3db94c15ae8eb5a9&lt;/tt&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
